desc=Welcome.
Did you hear the story? Master Jaime of the Divine Association in Roxbury will be requesting something to the adventurers. Not only Saints but anyone who can help him is welcome. The pay is not that bad, so you should go there, too.

Do you want to know, why I'm concerned of such things? I'm not concerned, it's just that Jaime asked me. Many people come and go here at the trading post, so it's the right place to make an advertisement.
runDlg=Jaime is on the other side of the town. Search carefully before asking anybody.
finishDlg=You came after hearing from Jeremiah. Thank you.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Talk with Jaime
