</newversion></questtextxml></ac1gt11a><ac1gt11b><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Bring back the Broken Pieces of Rough Snake Statues
desc=What I'm about to ask you to do is related to this world. Since the foxes began to attack people suddenly,  our Divine Association did several investigations. What we found out is that the strange statues placed in the Cardiff Abandoned Mine might be the cause. We guess that the statues shaped like a snake head carry a clue about the strange force of Cardiff Abandoned Mine.

For a closer investigation, I would like you to destroy the Snake Statues in  Cardiff Abondoned Mine and bring me Broken Pieces of it. 
runDlg=I've heard that it's somewhere in the middle of the Cardiff Abandoned Mine.
finishDlg=Thank you for helping. Phew&#x2026;Creatures from the dungeon changing...
They were once children of the nature, breathing in the energy of the forest... So sad this is the only way&#x2026;
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Bring back the Broken Pieces of Rough Snake Statues
