</newversion></questtextxml></ac1gt11b><ac1gt11c><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Deliver the letter to Lord Lionel
desc=(With a broken piece on one hand, Jaime closes his eyes and concentrates)

Oh my, we were right! There's great evil in this thing. My hand is still shaking. Because of this, foxes changed to attack people recklessly. This statue is turning them violent.

Thank you very much for helping us. Since I already expected this worst result, I prepared a letter.

Would you deliver this letter to Lord Lionel? He has to know the truth. 
runDlg=I hope the Lord will be smart.
finishDlg=The Master of the Divine Association of our city sent this letter? Hmm&#x2026; Something dangerous is happening in Roxbury. I got it. I will investigate about this, then you can go now.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Deliver the letter to Lord Lionel
