desc=I heard that there is a powerful person to support Lord Lionel. It was you!

Until now what you did was the destruction of evidence for investigation by Divine Association...... Roderick and Lord Lionel, as they failed the experiment for life in Cardiff, they destroyed evidence of their experiment and fierce animals.
You were used by them, not knowing anything.....

The reason for still trusting you?
We are the Divine Association. We can read and talk to your soul. But we can't restore things that already passed.

Pretend you don't know anything and go to Lord Lionel and tell him that Jamie of the Divine Association is really disappointed. Please help me.
runDlg=Even though we can't turn back time we can always try to fix future. Please help us so our future will not change to darkness.
finishDlg=Hahaha&#x2026; Did Jamie say that? Did you come here to say that? Thank you. You are a trusty friend. Forget everything and go back, take some rest now. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Talk to Lord Lionel
