</newversion></questtextxml></ac1gt13e><ron000001><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Deliver Ash's letter to Nadine in Ron
desc=Hmm... What should I do...

You ask what's happening?
In fact I have a sister in Ron, north of Roxbury. Actually that's my hometown.
However, since last month, letters that have always arrived, are not coming in.

I'm worried that something might have happened since there are monsters near Ron these days. If you have any plans to go to Ron, would you give this to my sister?

Ah! My sister's name is Nadine.
runDlg=It's already been a month&#x2026;
Thank you&#x2026;
finishDlg=Ash asked you?
It's a letter from Ash. Thank you so much.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Deliver Ash's letter to Nadine in Ron
