desc=It says I should write more often because he's worried. He's still a small kid and he's worried about me...

Actually there's no ship that can deliver letters to Ron.
There's a sea called The Sea of Bone above Ron and a month ago a girl entered the island but hasn't come back. The people who went to explore the island with the girl haven't come back either...

In fact, my parents went with them on the exploration. So I'm waiting here all day for the people... for my parents to come back.

Ah! I only talked about myself. You came all the way because of me and I haven't served you properly...

I'm sorry but would you go to Bessy the blacksmith? She will give you food if you show her this memo.
runDlg=I hope Ash doesn't worry...
finishDlg=Hello.
It's been a while since we had customers.
