desc=I've heard that you helped Nadine.

...

I guess she has told you about this and that.
In fact, Ron is a small island and it is not abundant.

About a month ago, a girl came by. She offered a lot of money and recruited people who would help her explore the Sea of Bone. Everybody was surprised of such an amount of money and participated in the exploration...
No one came back. As the girl left...

Oops! Forget what I just said. I just can't...

If you're really curious, give this memo to Lloyd the Bartender...
I will follow his decision.
runDlg=Don't ask anymore.
finishDlg=May I help you?
Bessy gave you this memo?
