desc=God... Bessy has left me with a difficult decision.
Anyways, if anyone saw you entering this island you are in danger, so I'll tell you.

When she left the island, she showed us the mark of a pirate, asking us to keep quiet and probably the other people who also left must have had other purposes.
And soon after she entered the Sea of Bone, pirate ships blocked the sea. With only the small ships that are left, we couldn't go call for help nor save the people from the Sea of Bone.

Since you seem to have a strong ship, would you go and see if there's anyone alive?
runDlg=Thank you very much.

The Sea of Bone is north of Ron.
finishDlg=Haven't seen an outsider for a while.
How did you get here?
