desc=Lloyd sent you? He's risking his own life.
Well, we are not captured by pirates but we are trapped in this place.

Since you've come all the way here, I'll tell you everything I know...

In fact, all the pirate ships you've encountered are disguised battleships. Don't know where they belong to but that'll be revealed through the battle. They pursued to kill all of us. Actually, if it weren't for that lady who told us about this place, we might have been all dead. However, we lost many men on our way to the island so we got trapped here.

I don't know what those ships were trying to protect in this island and why they attacked us but I sensed something bad.
That girl is keeping quiet... She might tell you, who has passed through all those ships, so would you like to talk to her?

Ah! Her name is Tasha.
runDlg=The lady has gone through a lot. She doesn't easily tell what's on her mind.
finishDlg=Uh... Hello? 
What brought you here?
