desc=Don't go too deep into the island. And could you bring me back anything you find from the monsters, that was used by a person?

And there's one thing you must be very careful of. There are monsters that generate supersonic waves around this place. If you attack them without caution all the monsters nearby will jump upon you.

As far as I know, Little One-eyed Bats generate supersonic waves.
runDlg=If you find anything during your investigation that was used by a person, please bring it to me.

Little One-eyed Bats are dangerous. Especially, when there are other monsters around them, don't try to do anything. 
finishDlg=These are... Elisa...
