desc=My sister has been experimented on with some stuff, after she was brought here.
It's been a while since she wrote her journal, so this is no useful hint.

I will most likely never find my sister, but I'm going to get rid of those hideous monsters.

Get out of here quickly. With your skills, you can go back to Ron with everybody.

Thank you so much. I can't give you anything nice, but this is something in return.

Also I'll give you this. If you go to Castle Hall by any chance, give this to Groop the shipbuilder. He will give you something that might help you on your journey.
runDlg=I've lost everything... All that is left now is my revenge.
finishDlg=This is... Tasha's handwriting... Tasha says that she received so much help... Thank you for helping her. Take this... It's a small reward. Now forget about us and keep on with your adventure. We will be glad to see you again someday... But life is not that easy, you know.
