</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Deliver Nadine's gift to Ash in Roxbury
desc=Oh my... You came back from the entrance because the Sea of Bones was too wild? Geez... You're weak...

If you have any change to go to Roxbury would you deliver this box to Ash? And also tell him that he's way too young to care about his elder sister... Hee hee.
runDlg=I wish you luck on your voyage.
finishDlg=Ah! My sister's letter and gift! Here, take this. The letter says that this gift is yours.
Everything's alright in Ron... Now I can work without being worried. Thank you so much..
</newversion></questtextxml></goroxber3><bc1gt21a><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Deliver Reptile's Liver
desc=Hey, you! Come here for a second.
How is it? It smells good, right? I am cooking a delicious chicken meal. It is my family's secret recipe. I learned it directly from my mother. You would not taste anything like this anywhere, not even in any noble countries.

However, there is a little problem. I am missing ingredients for my recipe. I can't leave the oven. I have to watch the fire.

What do I mean? It's obvious. You go buy the ingredients for me and I will pay you. Don't worry, I will keep my promise.
Well, let's see... I need 24 Reptile's Livers. You told me you would help, right? Then hurry up before I screw up my food. Go!
runDlg=Where are Reptiles? How do I know? Go near Tulach Dungeon. There should be some. Whatever&#x2026;
finishDlg=What took you so long? I will pay you, but I almost screw up my food. Thanks anyway.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Deliver Reptile's Liver
