desc=Welcome. We (The Royal Navy) kept an eye on you after you solved the problem of the Black Icon. You did many things here, therefore the Lord will give you an important task.

Your job is to find Admiral Harker. Until now, it was hard to get inside Tulach and observe it, because of the monsters and the impact of the Black Icon. There was a limit to the access to the dungeon. However, since the Black Icon is destroyed, we can go deeper into the dungeon for observation. Therefore, we decided to ask you to observe about Admiral Harker.

We all know that he died in the dungeon, but we want to know what took his life there. The only evidence is this little piece of metal one explorer brought a long time ago. I am sure it is a piece from the Admiral's badge. However, this is not enough evidence. We need more evidence to perfectly know about his death.

You catch the monsters and interrogate them. The monsters always take a piece of materials from their victims as a luck charm. They might have some stuff belonging to Admiral Harker. So far, our investigation told us that the admiral safely entered the first basement floor. The monsters must have been very strong, because the Admiral's soldiers died too. Obviously, we will pay you when you complete the mission.   
runDlg=As I told you before, we assume that Admiral Harker died on the first basement.
finishDlg=You really brought them. Well done. Let me see. I knew it! Thank you. Now, everything became much clearer. What is clear? I will tell you now.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collect Admiral Harker's treasure 
