desc=You remember the little metal piece I've shown you before. The piece is rotten, but because it is too small, we don't know why. However, the other pieces have the same rotten mark. As you know well, this mark cannot be caused by an ordinary attack.

We know that Admiral Harker got killed, but why did the golden badge break into pieces? And it is strange that the pieces got rotten. But the military cannot analyze it itself. We need help from the expert of poison, but people won't talk to the Royal Navy.

So would you like to help us? I will lend you the piece. Please find some expert and talk about it. How does this sound?
runDlg=The expert of poison would be... either dock managers or market managers
finishDlg=About poison? Of course I know. Because we sell medicine, we know about the ingredients of medicine. We need to know about poison because we need to know the antibiotic for poison.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Get information about poison from the expert
