desc=Huh? You need to know what kind of poison is on that piece? If we drop this in medical liquid... it's strange. If the piece is rotten this much, it should be acid poison, but it doesn't look like it. It does not even stink.
What the... This is not a poison. At least it is not an ordinary poison.

Don't look at me like that. It is true. I've never seen something like that before either. It looks more like the piece melted in fire. If this green part turns black, it looks exactly like a melted metal piece.

What do you think? Look at this. There is a piece of fabric on the metal piece. It is weird that this fabric piece was burnt to ashes. So any poison on the metal piece shoud be melted away as well. Like you said, it could be the power of magic. Good guess.  
runDlg=I don't have anything else to say. Now go.
finishDlg=You look a little tired. Did you get the information we need?
