desc=(You told Lennon Pepper's story) Did Pepper say that? It is more like fire than poison? How could it be...?
Now I get it when you talked about the magic fire.

By the way, there is a report about this matter. Since the power of the dark magic has been reduced, more explorers go deep into Tulach dungeon, and some of them said that they saw some strange books. The big book's cover is decorated with jewels. Those people who tried to touch it died. The witness said, that they suffered from the fire and eventually got burnt alive to death.

I think it matches with Pepper's story. The Admiral must have been burnt to death when he tried to get the book. He must have thought the book was just a treasure.

We should report this to General Renfield. Here is the envelope with the report in it. Please deliver this to General Renfield.
runDlg=You better hurry up. It is really important.
finishDlg=What is up? Lennon's report? Let me see that.
