desc=Would you like to work at the trading market? The trading market only cares about the order of trading materials, but it really needs help from explorers.

A part of Seahorse Stones has been missing from the trading market. It was kept in a storage, but there was a hole on the floor of the storage. Something stole the Seahorse Stones through this hole. This is crazy.

There was a rumor that it involves a professional thief or a conspirer. However, when we investigated the storage, there was a strange looking package. It was a package which is wrapped in a way that the Ghoulach from Gloshire do. 

In the Magistri, a reward is set out for the Ghoulach. Please catch these Ghoulach for us.
runDlg=Thank you. Do your best.
finishDlg=There is a slight problem. So I was thinking of another request.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunting Ghoulach
