</newversion></questtextxml></cc1gt28a><cc1gt28b><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Clear out Ravenous Ghoulach
desc=Seems that the Ghoulach broke into the storage by the order of Bluegangsters. They must have needed the Ravenous Ghoulach to penetrate the hard floor.  We are glad that we caught the Ghoulach this time, but the Bluegangsters could recruit the Ghoulachs and Ravenous Ghoulachs again for breaking in and stealing our Seahorse Stones.

As much as we would like to do it, but we can't make the whole ground out of metal.

Therefore, we would like to ask you a favor. You need to show the Bluegangsters how dangerous it is to come to the storage for stealing. It sounds a little harsh, but if we don't show it, they will always come back with the Ravenous Ghoulach. We can't afford that. We cannot keep paying people a lot of money for bringing back our materials. You just have to scare the heck out of the Ravenous Ghoulach. About 20 of them.
runDlg=We will wait here with your money.
finishDlg=Thank you. Tyler is looking for you. You should go and see Tyler.
