desc=How have you been? It is an honor for you to meet the legend of adventure, myself, Tyler.

Heh, you look confused. I guess you never met the legend in real.
What? You never heard of me? Hahaha-
Maybe you are new to the city. Otherwise, how could you not know about me. Did you come for my autograph?
Huh? Gladys? Oh, it's about the work.

When I analyzed the Seahorse Stones, I found another stone in the package.
Look at this. This stone is different from the Seahorse Stones. Only nobles know how to use Seahorse Stones. This new stone is printed in a unique pattern and a clear jewel is attached to it.

This is Gloshire Cobalt Stone. There is no special characteristic to this stone, but because of this unique blue color, it is used for decoration for a lot of weapons or other decoration purposes. However, there is mucus on the stone.

I, the great Tyler, got it at first sight. I am sure this mucus is from Ghoulach.

 Now, can you guess what I am going to ask you? Right, I want you to help reserving these stones from them. They are very strong monster, so are you ready for it.

Me? Of course, I could get rid of them just with my pinky, but I am too busy so I can't go. So don't bother me, I will pay you a lot as reward.
runDlg=They are very violent so be careful.
finishDlg=Oh, thank you. You should brag about that you had a chance to work with me. Oh, here is your money.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collect Gloshire Cobalt Stone from Groot Ghoulach
