desc=Seeing you standing there, I wonder if you're looking for a job. No, I don't have a specific reason for asking you this. I just heard Marigold at the pub was looking for a worker. So I ask you, because you looked like someone who might want it. She is very professional so she will pay you good money.

Go up the stairs to the west of the habor, then you will see her. Tell her that I sent you, then she will tell you about the job. Go.
runDlg=Don't you know where Marigold is? She is west of the habor in the city. Look for her as you go upstairs.
finishDlg=Welcome~ No money~ no food. This is Marigold's bar. HOHOHO~
