Mission2=Report to Ruskin
desc=Did Ruskin tell you I was looking for a helper? That's strange. It is true that I need a favor, but it is actually a favor for Ruskin. Looks like I pay you with jewels, but the truth is that Ruskin, doesn't like the Explorer Association anymore.

Why did he tell you that? Oh, I see. By using me, he tries to spread rumors around as many people as possible that the Explorer Association thinks the center of Gloshire is the Seahorse Stone producing mountain.

It is also for distracting its competition, the Noble Masquer for the Seahorse Stones. He did not tell me the real reason, just sending people up here. I can't just let this happen.

Anyway, a promise is a promise, so I will tell you the mission. You go to the center of Gloshire where could be Seahorse Stone-producing mountain located, to kill Skeleton Soldier which are obstacles for their plan.
Oh, and listen carefully. You don't have to report anything to me. A bad man who just uses people like him should experience failure at least once. Go and tell Ruskin.  
runDlg=Hurry up. It's only Skeleton Soldier. You can catch them, right?
finishDlg=Why did you come to me? Hmm... Did she say something like that? She kicked my bum this time. Anyways, I will pay you the money. Here you go.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Get rid of Skeleton Soldier
