desc=I underestimated Marigold. From now on, I should tell her every detail, when I ask her a favor. I made a mistake.

However, since it did not harm her in any way, I guess she does not have many complaints. It was not a bad or dangerous thing, plus I payed for the work. I am afraid that I need to sincerely ask her another favor this time.

Deliver this letter to her. If she asks what this is about, just tell her that it's my apology. You will not say this time that you don't know where Marigold is, will you? 
runDlg=Thank you. If she read my letter, she will be kind again.
