</newversion></questtextxml></cc1gt001><cc1gt002><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Collect the Material Box
desc=There was a burglary on the ocean in Exeter Island. While we were looking for a person to solve the problem, we remembered that Lennon told me you left for our city.

A few days ago, a ship which carried many materials was stranded at this ocean on the way to Glostern. Probably, the coward steerman sailed the ship too close to the Island, trying to avoid the monsters. The captain want at least to deliver the materials, so the Magistri sent people to the place.

However, there were no materials left when we went to the place the ship was stranded. There were only footprints of humans around the ship. Maybe those footprints are bluegangsters'.

They might have come like a bunch of crows which saw gold. I am sure that bluegangsters stole the materials. Luckily there is an insurance on those materials. However, the problem is that the materials are specially ordered from the shipbuilding company. The company needs them immediately.

Please go and kill the bluegagnsters and bring the Material Box.
runDlg=Hum? Did you bring back the cargo? Bluegangsters live in Gloshire. Be prepared, but don't take too long. Please hurry up.
finishDlg=You brought back the cargo. It's still sealed with the stamp. Great! We can just use them right away without washing the salt off them. Your reputation was right.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collect the Material Box
