desc=Since the five Islands had their own cities before the Florensia kingdom was established, Exeter Island was the central city in the human world.
Back then, Glostern played a role as intermediate trading dock. During the 5 years-war, our navy activity was reduced, and Bergruen was starting having dominance. If that didn't happen, Glostern would have thrived a lot more.

It is my wish that Glostern will become the center of the kingdom. Luckily, there are rumors about that there are many magic stones in Gloshire so there are many visitors lately.

I ran out of materials for fixing ships because there are so many ships coming. Kevin in the shipbuilding company is also worried about that. Now, take this Material Box to Kevin. He will be really happy. 
runDlg=Kevin thinks it is his fault when he sees ships with damaged masts and wrecks. I know he is a hard worker, but he thinks too much.
finishDlg=I am sorry. We ran out of materials so I can't fix the ship. Oh, can you show me that box? Oh my... These are the materials I ordered. I thought I would never get them. Thank you very much. Now I can fix ships again.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Deliver to Kevin
