desc=Do you know that the Royal Navy started their investigation again about Tulach Dungeon in Magnel Island?

Not long ago, one of the marines from Magnel Island asked me if there exist monsters similar the ones inside of Tulach Dungeon. Therefore, I told him, "I don't know much about the cultural heritage, but we have the great explorer named Tyler in our city. He will tell you every single secret in a minute."

However, he did not believe me. People from military always doubt everything. I was mad so I asked Tyler to investigate Gloshire and he said he would do it, saying "It's a piece of cake." However, I haven't heard anything from him yet. Please go ask Tyler about the investigation. 
runDlg=Did you hear that Tyler went out on a boat to the sea to catch the giant sea monster, Crwbarff only with one spear? It is said that there is another Crwbarff, a brother of the dead one living in the sea. I am not sure if that is true.  
finishDlg=Hey, did you handle the shields with care? You have to take good care of them because not everyone can have this much muscles like me. Anyways, what's up?
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Talk to Tyler
