desc=You are not from my village. Are you an explorer? Kevin sent you? I don&#x2019;t know why he picked you among many other explorers. Not like I care though.

Why I'm out here alone? Why are you asking me that? I am sorry that I screamed. I have something to find... No, it's nothing.

There are ravenous monsters called Ghoulach in Gloshire. I came to collect Ghoulach's spines. I was chasing Ghoulachs, but I got surrounded by them. I almost lost my life but I managed to escape.

Now, just as I was taking a rest, you showed up. So you understand why I screamed so loud, right?

God, it is almost time to go back, but I could not collect the amount of spines I need... not even half as many as I need. Plus, I think I injured my knee when I ran away.

Could you please collect the spines for me? If you do this for me, I will pay you a big amount when you come back to the village.
runDlg=The Ravenous Ghoulach is different from the regular Ghoulach. They are nothing. Just think of them as hungry dogs. A few years ago, they would be nothing to me, but it looks like I'm getting old...
finishDlg=(Klaus hides something when he saw people coming)
Did you collect them all? You are greater than I thought. Thank you.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collect Ravenous Ghoulach's Spine
