desc=Look at this. The hunters of the Explorer Association caught Blue Gangsters and found these things. Don't they look like broken pieces of a vase or rock? I know that they have a strong self-interest, Blue Gangsters steal everything in sight, but I never heard that they steal something like that.

According to the hunters, Blue Gangster keep these pieces with care. I think these pieces have something to do with their power.

However, nobody listens to me, except for Lilian. She said that she is willing to help me to investigate this, if I am too busy.
I was so happy. She looks like a cold person because she doesn't talk much, but in fact, she is very kind.

Well, I need more stuff for my investigation. So please go to Gloshire and collect Pottery Pieces from Naar and Stone Pieces. Then carry the stuff to Lilian.
runDlg=Who made the Gloshire heritage? Where are they gone?
finishDlg=What's up this time? Those pieces are... You are the explorer who tries to investigate with Elsy? You are the most serious man I've ever met. Thank you for your help. 
