desc=Did they set the campground on the area of the weremole's surveillance tower?
That Magistri&#x2026; always causing trouble everywhere.

That surveillance tower was built when weremoles fought the Merfolk in Gloshire. Those absurd weremoles destructed the Merfolk's heritage and built the tower there. The stones used for the tower are parts of the Merfolk's sacred altars. The Vismann were created by Merfolk and consider the Merfolk as it's ancestors.

Well, how would they feel when they saw people making a campground on that place? I will send guards right away to escort the investigators to Glostern.

You need to do one thing as well. You have to go to the campground in Daigon Hill which the Magistri's investigators built and terminate it. We should not provoke the Vismann anymore.   
runDlg=I have to talk to the Magistri about this matter. Did you terminate the campground? If anything remains in the area of the tower, Vismann will attack people again, being provoked by it. 
finishDlg=Well done. Although the intention wasn't bad, it does not always end up the right way. This will be a good lesson to the Magistri.
