desc=Have you been to the Fox Den? It was an important channel between Larksdowns and Weed Ridge, but now it is a heavenly place for the monsters.

When I was young, it was the most comfortable place. There were my secret places where I used to sleep when it was hot. My parents often looked for me when I fell asleep there. They thought I got kidnapped.
Oh, by the way, I secretly took two boxes of candles from my dad's store and brought them to the Fox Den. From what I heard, Slavefoxes and Fox Bathunters are using candles out of the boxes these days. Damn them. Who allowed them to use the candles?

If you don't mind, can you bring my candles back from them? I don't mind the used ones. I need about twelve candles. Please do me a favor.
runDlg=Hmn&#x2026; warm Fox Den&#x2026; comfortable atmosphere&#x2026;. I miss it&#x2026;(She's standing asleep)
finishDlg=Oh my god! You brought them. Let me see. It is right. There is my dad's symbol printed at the bottom of the candle. This is the correct candle. Thank you.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collect Slavefox's Candle
Mission2=Collect Fox Bathunter's Candle
