desc=It seems that you know much of it. Don't worry. I don't have plans to report to the Lord.

Don't reproach us noble. What our noble did was struggling to have a power for facing evil. We felt the coming of something big and dark. It was too strong to be opposed by humans alone.

The experiment failed terribly, so we have to destroy everything for the safety of Roxbury. The last experiment is in the deepest place of 2nd Basement of Fox Den.

Destroy the work of failure called Lanoir and bring it's tail. It means information and warning for other nobles in other places. Please do me a favor.
runDlg=Watch those sharp claws and teeth. Since his body has been accustomed to the power of the darkness, he probably possesses the great dark power.
finishDlg=You came back safely. I can sense the dark power coming out of your backpack.
