desc=Magnel Island has a long history related to the establishment of Florensia kingdom. It is well known that the previous king, Gerhart and the Dark Captain of the Pirates, Wenceslas had a secret meeting at Magnel Island. The five-year war, so called Black Dragon fort war had a miraculous turning point due to the navy fight between Magnel Island and Exeter Island.

For a long time, Magnel Island has played a role as a fort very well because of its location between Cardiff Island and Exeter Island. If you look at the greatly high wall around Castle Hall, you could tell it is more like a fort than a city. Soldiers from Castle Hall usually have trained here for guarding the fort and work in the military under my order.

Moreover, we ask explorers to get rid of the monsters to keep Castle Hall a safer place. If you want to stay in Castle Hall, you better pay more attention to where you're going in Castle Hall than in Exeter or Cardiff Island. It is hard for weak explorers to get used to be here on the island.
runDlg=Well... My story is kind of done, but wait for a minute
finishDlg=I would like to test what kind of great explorer you are. If you pass the test, I guarantee you a high pay. Are you interested in it?
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Talk to General Renfield
