desc=Well&#x2026; As I told you, always all great explorers come to Magnel Island, where Castle Hall is located, to prove their skills. However, the truth is - it is hard to find one great explorer among those many explorers. It looks great that Florensia appears to develop with those explorers, but the problem is that there are so many unqualified explorers. I saw many unqualified explorers lose their lives by the monsters.

Well, if my insight of humans has not gone that bad yet, I could tell that you are different from them. However, that's not for sure. Therefore, I'd like to test you a little.

There are giant bees called Hornet and Queen Hornet on the way to Tulach Dungeon in Castle Field. They are not that dangerous, but there are so many of them. Therefore, we kill them only from time to time. Those monsterous bees will occupy the island. So please go kill some of them and bring their wings as proof. If you complete the mission, I will give you a small gift as my approval. Take care. 
runDlg=To prove your qualification, you need to bring ten Hornet's Poisoned Stings and Four Wings of Queen Hornet.
finishDlg=Oh- you came back safely. My insight has not gone bad at all. Well done. Sure you are an extraordinary explorer. I will ask you more favors later. Pick one of these items, it's a reward!
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collect Hornet's Poison Sting
Mission2=Collect Queen Hornet's Wings
