desc=Lesser Imp was not a monster we could easily see in Castle Field. Only many similar monsters live in Tulach Dungeon. However, Lesser Imps have started to show up one by one in Castle Field. They may be smaller than the other monsters, but stronger and dangerous. Because of them, we had to double our guard for shipping people who collects safety materials. They have to go to Castle Field soon again for collection.

If anyone could kill some of the monsters, we do not have to increase the number of guards. Would you like to do that for us? We will reward you with some of the expenses we spend for protection.   
runDlg=Don't work too hard. We would like you to kill only eight of them. Please do us the favor.
finishDlg=Oh, welcome back. Well done. Now, we will go and collect some good materials, so we are capable to invent more great items.
