desc=Do you know about the Tulach Temple which you can enter from north of Castle Field? There are so many stories about the Tulach Temple that we can't even tell which story is true. At least one thing is for sure, that such a temple did not exist 200 years ago. It just popped out of nowhere.

However, in that devastated land, the monsters called Draug gathered together and rebuilt the temple. Then they made that area their homeland. On top of it, the Draug caught every monster and plant and changed them into a weird form by using their dark magic.

Now because of Draug and the other monsters, the Tulach Temple turned into a dangerous place where other species and explorers cannot freely enter. The Tulach Temple which should not even exist, now became the biggest problem in Magnel Island.

Well, seeing is believing. There is a rumor that there are many magic stones and weapons piled up there. If you are a true explorer, you should be interested.

First of all, it is important to study everything about the monsters, so you should carefully check out the first floor. Then, as the study about Draug, you should fight Draug Warriors and Draug Servant which are classified as the lowest rank of Draug. 
runDlg=You know where the Tulach Temple is, right? Its entrance is north of Castle Field. 
finishDlg=This is only the beginning. You should get ready for the real stuff. Although the Tulach Temple is a dangerous place, we will go and explore it because there are many mysterious secrets and items. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunt Draug Warrior
Mission2=Hunt Draug Servant
