desc=You are the person who often visits Tulach Dungeon, right? Then I will ask you a favor.

There are monsters called Carreg and Merrow in Tulach dungeon. Carreg is the moving statue made out of a special magic stone by the Draug for guarding their dungeon. It is hard to fight it, because it is very strong and hard, depending on they're made out of stones. Moreover, Merrow used to be the spirit of the small lake near the dungeon. However, Draugs captured and contaminated it with the dark magic, so those poor spirits with the magic stone on their forehead are controlled by Draugs.

I've always wondered what kind of magic stone is used to build the statues and control the lake spirits. However, there was no one until today who could kill Carregs and Merrows and bring the stones of them. So I am going to ask you for this favor, since I heard you check out the dungeon often lately.

If possible, please bring both bipolar magic stones of Carreg and Merrow so I could analyze them. For an explorer like you, it would not be a very difficult task, wouldn't it?  
runDlg=You can find Carreg and Merrow on the first floor in Tulach Dungeon. Perhaps, you can see them in the basement, but that is a very dangerous place.
finishDlg=These are the magic stones. I could feel that the power from these magic stones is different from the power from normal magic stones. This stone could possibly be used in ancient times. If I am correct, these stones will be very useful. This is not much, but please accept my money.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collect Carreg's Magic Stone
