desc=OK. It's time for the revenge. I will request two things from you.

For one, catch Draug Brenin, the leader of the hateful Draugs. No need to explain more about it, right? If you catch the leader of the Draugs, it means our victory over them. It will also end my revenge.

One more thing... Another explorer told me, that he saw a monster called Stone Knight using some kind of spear with a strange picture. The picture looks like a burning key. Being impressed, he brought one of these spears to me, and I realized that it was my missing colleague's spear.

It means that our soldiers died in the cold basement of the temple and the monsters are using their weapons. I am not sure that having something to remember them makes me feel any better, but I would like you to collect more stuff, belonging to my colleagues, from Stone Knights, especially things belonging to my three best friends.

Did you get it? Please catch Stone Knight and collect three rusty spears for me and also catch Draug Brenin, the leader of the Draugs. Then my revenge shall be completed.      
runDlg=Don't forget! Only you could complete my revenge. The mission will be wasted if you fail either killing Draug Brenin or collecting the three spears.
finishDlg=(Geronimo shakes his hand with the three spears in it) I don't know how to ever thank you. Not only did you finish my revenge, but you also set the poor souls free. Now I feel much lighter. No reward would be enough for what you have done. However, please take one of these weapons. I selected the best ones. Please accept the gift from the bottom of my heart.
