desc=I have a very confidential request.

In the past I heard a story from my father, it's about our Avery family.
There is an evil place in the grand Avery family mansion. But I couldn't hear more details. Therefore, I have been researching about this mansion in the meantime. In this town I wasn't able to find anything else but the normal entrance to the mansion. But recently I found an entrance on the other side of the town.

Go outside of the town and turn to the west side, to a ruined maze, called the Maze of Lion.
There you will find an entrance which connects to the underground. I think it might pass the mountain range and connect to the underground of the mansion.

I heard that there were strong guardians to protect the secret. Would you find that place and check the existance of these guardians?
runDlg=If you leave the town and go to the west, there is the Maze of Lion.
finishDlg=So guardians really exist? The problem is, what now.&#x2026; Anyway thank you for your efforts.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Destroy 8 Shrineguard Spearman
Mission2=Destroy 8 Shrineguard Knight
