Outside of town, Ghosts are showing up. Weird rumors are spreading around, therefore, since it's a task of the Divine Association to keep faith, we should check.

 The rumors indicate the appearance of Ghosts is located in the area in the middle of the Maze of Deadman in the west. People saw Ghosts coming out of the door which leads to the basement. Anyhow I am suspicious about the entrance.

