desc=From time to time weird reports are coming to the Divine Association.

Outside of town, Ghosts are showing up. Weird rumors are spreading around, therefore, since it's a task of the Divine Association to keep faith, we should check.

Rumors about the appearance of Ghosts are spreading out to the area in the middle of the Maze of Deadman in the west outside of town. People saw Ghosts coming out of the door which leads to the basement. Anyhow I am suspicious about the entrance.

Would you find that entrance and research of existance of Ghosts?
runDlg=From the recent rumor, there is something in the underground pathway .
finishDlg=Oh dear! The rumor was real&#x2026; Something had happened at that time, therefore, it's not strange that monsters are appearing... Ah, forget what I just said.
</newversion></questtextxml></ehouse002><ehouse003><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Hunt Stone Watcher
desc=Now we don't have problems eating and living, but we can't make lots of money with only necessaries. The market is not bustling, compared with the past, because everybody in town is only attracted to the interesting case.

But recently I heard good news. A secret door, which allows us to go around the town, has been found. Yet that secret door is connected to the mansion of the noble Avery family.
The rumor that they operated a secret laboratory for whatever reason in the past was true.

I don't know the details but the important thing is, that a rare animal was found there. I don't know how they found it, but the very peculiar animal was caught. Seeing that, all the town became a mess. It looks very wild but popular enough to catch. People call it Stone Watcher.

As talented people, who can go into Underground Laboratory are rare, I trust you to catch some of them.
runDlg=For you who likes adventure, it's worth to do. Also I can make money.
finishDlg=Haha, you did a good job. Work must be tough. Are the monsters in there strong?
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunt Stone Watcher
