desc=After you confirmed the existence of Ghosts, the Divine Association checked the Underground Laboratory accurately. We didn't check enough on the inside, but we knew by going deeper into it from the entrance, the influence of darkness was getting severe. Even though Ghosts near the entrance still have a pure feeling of human itself, if they get influenced by the darkness more and more, they might be changed to being out of control.

Would you find some Maid of Dark which were exposed to darkness and destroy them?
runDlg=I expect they are deeper into the laboratory than the spot at which the Ghost Maids were found.
finishDlg=You did a good job. By the way, the situation there looks more severe than expected .
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunt Maid of Dark
