desc=I was told that you know the Underground Laboratory of the Avery mansion very well. That place has a history for us noble. Not only ourselvess but all the towns were involved with this place. Keep the detailed story for later, I have something to check this time.

In the past, there was a time, when lots of people were missing in this town. We couldn't find a trace of them in any other places. Would you search for traces in Underground Laboratory? Most of them were maids who worked for nobles as servants. It should be not that difficult to search for them. I hope you can find them.
runDlg=If they are in the Underground Laboratory, they must have changed to monsters, just like the other monsters. Getting rid of them and doing a research is fine.
finishDlg=There&#x2026;.They were still there. I thought they were sealed. It's a big problem.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Destroy Ghost Maid 
Mission2=Destroy Maid of Dark
desc=I was told that you know the Underground Laboratory of the Avery mansion very well. That place has a history for us noble. Not only us but also all the towns were involved with this place. Keep the detailed story for later, I have something to check this time.

In the past, there was a time, when lots of people were missing in this town. We couldn't find a trace of them in any other places. Would you search their traces in Underground Laboratory? Most of them are maids who worked for nobles as servants, they are not that difficult to search. I hope you can find them.
runDlg=If they are in the Underground Laboratory, they must be changed to monsters, just like the other monsters. Getting rid of them and doing a research is fine.
finishDlg=There&#x2026;.They were still there. I thought they were sealed. It's a big problem.
</newversion></questtextxml></ehouse005><ehouse008><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Get rid of Nelia
desc=You are curious about the underground laboratory.

Actually, the maids you have seen were not missing. At that time Lord Avery, father of Lady Avery, and I were collaborating in a secret experiment. That experiment was happening in the underground laboratory of the mansion. That experiment was about increasing the dark side of noble magic.
At that time, many maids participated in that experiment.

However, the experiment failed. At this time, the Divine Association also started to be suspicious of it.
To make it even worse, the traitors who planned on destroying the city were known.

We hastily tried to seal the laboratory to prevent such a thing, but we could not save all the Maids, polluted by the experiments back outside before we sealed it... Although all of this happened for the sake of Glostern, we were shocked by such an utterly ill result.

Until today I am suffering from terrible feelings of guilt whenever thinking of the maidens, locked away in the Underground Laboratory. Especially Nelia, who helped me a lot in the past...

Would you help me, searching for Nelia and letting her poor soul rest in peace?  
runDlg=Actually, other people have to feel more responsibility.
finishDlg=Now I am a little bit relieved. But, my duty just starts here.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Get rid of Nelia
