desc=Now in full scale, we have to erase these faults of the past.

Not only that nobles had a prudent position in the past experiment, but also some new noble, who fell into the experiment itself, started to rise. They are the people who foster to overcome the limits of magic.

But there was a side effect. They have to absorbe blood. Finally they threw out the heart of a nomal human and entered into the road of vampires. They formed the Zerg, a strong vampire troop, following them like hands and feet...

If you can find out their traces, you will get the clue of corrupted noble.
runDlg=Anyhow, what protects the town from them are our noble. We made shrine guardians and sealed the entrance.
finishDlg=As I expected, they are seizing the Underground Laboratory. From now on, it's time for a full scale of fight.
