desc=Finally I found the reason for all this evil.

Many noble who participated in the underground experiments had chosen the road of vampires for extravagant reasons.

 For magic experiments in the underground, I appointed a trusted person as a research manager and created a Baron. That man has great magic power but is pure as a boy. Everybody called him Little Baron and liked him. Among them Lady Rose, having a powerful family origin, was very close to him and people called her Little Rose.

 But she became a witch, which called disaster.

 The young noble, captive by her vividness, started to follow her unconditionally. Finally Little Rose, fascinated with the sensational charm of the experiments, overcame the limit of the experiment with agitating people following her. Now she stands in the center of vampire nobles.

You must get rid of her.
runDlg=If you are captivated by her, it will be a problem.
finishDlg=She and the people following her will appreciate you.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Get rid of Little Rose
