desc=The rumor that the Magistri were related to the conspiracy is spreading in the town as it was true. Especially I got focused as a leader of that conspiracy.

It's all past, but now I am in a situation to solve it. At that time, actually, the dangerous experiment that our Lord and the Noble Masquer lead together was impossible without support of our Magistri. Maegner, powerful supporter of the Magistri, was active. He argued to help a man of influence in town and expand the influence of the Magistri. But Maegner did more than support. He involved himself to the work of the Underground Laboratory.

That time Little Baron, appointed as a person in charge of Underground Laboratory, was recommended by Maegner. Maybe, there was a plan between Maegner and Little Baron.

Especially, Maegner started to bribe the Navy and tried to get the famous leader of pirates. They usually have power over common people's ability. I thought something was going wrong from that time.

At the time we started the experiment, the pressure from the Divine Association was getting stronger. As public opinion got worse, there was a movement to close the Underground Laboratory in a hurry. Therefor, I tried to lead the Mercenaries and protect them. The Magistri were related deeply, but they didn't discuss with us. I thought they made a false political decision.

But the result was miserable. A weird group, who were not on the noble's side and not on the merchant's side, showed up and destroyed us. They were experiment objects made by Maegner and little Baron. I should have destroyed Maegner at that time.

Now, find Maegner and destroy him. I have to find out what they did.
runDlg=Now we are getting along well with the noble. That's because we need their power and influence and they need our money.
finishDlg=So it's true. He already changed to a monster which lost all personality... Creating these monsters, I have become a monster myself.
