Mission2=Hunt Grim Reaper
desc=As you know, foxes in Larksdowns and Devil Walkers in Weed Ridge are one of the biggest problems for our city. Except for adventurers, people can't even pass those villages because the amount of monsters is increasing. At this point, the city guards and the adventurers killed some of the mosters, but it is no use unless the leader is captured.

Looks like you are superior to all the other adventurers I've ever seen. Would you try to hunt Silver Vixen, the leader of the foxes and Grim Reaper, the leader of the Devil Walkers?     
runDlg=Be careful! There should be many guarding monsters around the leader. Better come up with a good plan to approach them.
finishDlg=Perhaps, the monsters attack people because we kill them for their skin to use it for clothing materials, or what happened lately in the Fox Den caused them to do it. Anyway, we will see about that later. Well done.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunt Silver Vixen 
